===Etymology===
Along with {{och-l|剛|hard, firm, stiff}}, derived from the terminative of {{och-l|固|firm, solid, hard}}, literally "having become solid, hard" ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

For the identity of the unknown preinitial *''C'' reconstructed by {{zh-ref|Baxter & Sagart (2014)}}, compare the pre-syllable *''t-'' of {{cog|mkh-vie-pro|*t-kaːŋ}}, its reflex.

